SELECT    UNIX_TIMESTAMP(`time`) as `time`,
          PowerLevel1 as value,
          'US-1' as metric
FROM      SH2acUpstreamPowerLevel
WHERE     DeviceName = 'SH2ac' and
          $__timeFilter(`time`)
ORDER BY  `time` ASC
